This paper discusses the technical fundamentals and large-scale deployment potential of LPWA networks for IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the implementation examples and challenges faced in the field-test results, which could be related to information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), cybersecurity (cs.CR), and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
